Zar nije prelep dan?
- Bogami jeste.

888
01:23:59,280 --> 01:24:03,034
Mi to zovemo lažno prolece.

889
01:24:58,560 --> 01:25:00,278
Izvolite.

890
01:25:04,800 --> 01:25:07,189
Cašu.

891
01:25:07,360 --> 01:25:12,195
Mr Sweeney.
Hocete da okušate srecu?

892
01:26:29,080 --> 01:26:32,914
Prijatelju, za tebe.

893
01:26:34,280 --> 01:26:41,118
Da se malo raskomotiš.
- Pa, gospodine, ove stare kosti vam zahvaljuju.

894
01:26:43,400 --> 01:26:46,915
Nadam se da ce naici pravi momak.

895
01:27:23,080 --> 01:27:26,595
Roðendan mi je.
Daj mi najbolje šta imaš.

896
01:29:01,920 --> 01:29:05,629
Dovo ti je za Alberta.

897
